videos.description: Jalen Brunson fights through the contact and makes the and-1 jumper.
videos.headline: Nova's Brunson makes turnaround shot plus the foul

videos.description: Phil Booth misses the 3-pointer but Mikal Bridges rises up and slams home the putback dunk.
videos.headline: Nova's Bridges jams home the missed  shot

videos.description: Omari Spellman jumps and rejects the layup attempt.
videos.headline: Nova's Spellman rises up for big block

videos.description: Villanova uses the extra passes to set up Donte DiVincenzo in the corner for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Nova's great ball movement leads to DiVincenzo 3-pointer

videos.description: Donte DiVincenzo gets around the defender in transition with a nice move and scores the bucket.
videos.headline: Nova's DiVincenzo makes great move for layup

videos.description: Mikal Bridges makes the steal and passes it up to Donte DiVincenzo, who finishes in transition plus the foul.
videos.headline: Nova's steal turns into and-1 layup for DiVincenzo
